 400 REM === Player repeats ===
 410 LET r=21: GO SUB 3100: LET t$="Your turn!": INK 6: BRIGHT 1: GO SUB 3000: BRIGHT 0
 420 FOR i=1 TO LEN s$
 430 LET k$=INKEY$
 440 IF k$="" THEN GO TO 430
 450 IF k$="1" THEN GO SUB 2100: GO TO 500
 460 IF k$="2" THEN GO SUB 2200: GO TO 500
 470 IF k$="3" THEN GO SUB 2300: GO TO 500
 480 IF k$="4" THEN GO SUB 2400: GO TO 500
 490 GO TO 430
 500 REM === Check answer ===
 510 IF k$<>s$(i) THEN GO TO 700
 520 PAUSE 5
 530 IF INKEY$<>"" THEN GO TO 530
 540 NEXT i
 550 REM === Correct! ===
 560 LET score=score+1
 570 LET r=21: GO SUB 3100: LET t$="Correct! Score: "+STR$ score: INK 4: GO SUB 3000
 580 BEEP 0.15,20: BEEP 0.15,24
 590 PAUSE 30
 600 GO TO 200
 700 REM === Wrong! ===
 710 BEEP 0.5,-10
 720 BORDER 2: PAUSE 25: BORDER 0
 730 LET r=10: LET t$="WRONG!": INK 2: BRIGHT 1: FLASH 1: GO SUB 3000: FLASH 0: BRIGHT 0
 740 LET r=12: LET t$="Score: "+STR$ score: INK 5: GO SUB 3000
 750 LET r=14: LET t$="Sequence was "+STR$ (LEN s$)+" long": INK 7: GO SUB 3000
 760 STOP
